title: Republicans set to pass bill limiting John Doe probes
text: MADISON, Wis. (AP) - Wisconsin Republicans on Tuesday moved closer to dramatically restricting the secret John Doe techniques that investigators used against Gov. Scott Walker's campaign and his former aides, bringing a bill to the floor of both legislative houses that would prevent prosecutors from using the techniques to investigate ... ...
